# Exclude local dev env files from Docker build.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL must NOT be set in the production image.
# Without it, the compiled bundle uses relative paths (empty baseURL),
# which means API calls go to the same host/port the browser opened —
# the ALB — and work from any device, any network, any IP.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Other files not needed in the image
node_modules
.git
*.md
